{
  "page": "Lucifer Justman",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Justman\" title=\"House Justman\"><img alt=\"House Justman.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/House_Justman.svg/50px-House_Justman.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/House_Justman.svg/75px-House_Justman.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1b/House_Justman.svg/100px-House_Justman.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Lucifer Justman<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Liar</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Justman\" title=\"House Justman\"><img alt=\"House Justman.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/House_Justman.svg/50px-House_Justman.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/House_Justman.svg/75px-House_Justman.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1b/House_Justman.svg/100px-House_Justman.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/River_king\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"River king\">River king</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">King of the Trident</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lucifer Justman</b>, known as <b>Lucifer the Liar</b>, was a presumed member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Justman\" title=\"House Justman\">House Justman</a> living four centuries prior to <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lucifer_Justman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lucifer claimed the title of <a href=\"/index.php/River_king\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"River king\">river king</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">King of the Trident</a> in the generations after the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> were conquered by the <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Arlan_III_Durrandon\" title=\"Arlan III Durrandon\">Arlan III Durrandon</a>. Lucifer had a brief, inglorious reign before being put down by the power of <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>. His connection with the extinct <a href=\"/index.php/House_Justman\" title=\"House Justman\">Justman</a> dynasty is unconfirmed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lucifer_Justman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Riverlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404205312\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.104 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.522 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 472/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10925/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5459/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 343/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 567/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.260/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.49 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  508.971      1 -total\n 98.21%  499.850      1 Template:Infobox_monarch\n 97.62%  496.859      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.94%   55.673     14 Template:Infobox_value\n  2.17%   11.039      2 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.36%    6.934      1 Template:Ref\n  0.90%    4.561      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.39%    1.962      1 Template:References\n  0.23%    1.178      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18675-0!canonical and timestamp 2026040420